						               													<description>This game is about the character Spirit ('Szilaj' in Hungarian) and his friends from the Disney movie. The game is the card version of &amp;quot;Szilaj: Kalandok Miraderoban&amp;quot; (Spirit: Adventures in Miradero), which was published earlier in the same year, 2021.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;The mechanics of the game are simple: at the start of each round, you must turn over one more card than you are playing, and everyone from the current starting player picks one. There are a variety of cards on the table from which you can score points, and the type and suit of cards you collect in front of you is very important.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your goal will be to compose as clever combinations as possible to represent the characters, horses, objects and locations of our story. Using the beginner rule set, you'll quickly and easily master the basics of the game, which you can later deepen in the advanced mode with extra cards and new combinations. Mysterious secret missions will also be unlocked, giving you additional points at the end of the game if you complete them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whoever collects the most valuable deck of cards wins the game!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher (translated)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Original (Hungarian) description:&amp;#10;&amp;quot;A j&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;k mechanizmusa egyszer&amp;#197;&amp;#177;: minden k&amp;ouml;r elej&amp;eacute;n fel kell csapjatok eggyel t&amp;ouml;bb lapot, mint ah&amp;aacute;nyan j&amp;aacute;tszotok, &amp;eacute;s az aktu&amp;aacute;lis kezd&amp;#197;&amp;#145;j&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;kost&amp;oacute;l kezdve mindenki v&amp;aacute;laszt bel&amp;#197;&amp;#145;le egyet. Sokf&amp;eacute;le k&amp;aacute;rtya ker&amp;uuml;l az asztalra, amib&amp;#197;&amp;#145;l pontokat tudtok &amp;ouml;sszegy&amp;#197;&amp;#177;jteni, &amp;eacute;s nagyon fontos, hogy milyen t&amp;iacute;pus&amp;uacute; &amp;eacute;s sz&amp;iacute;n&amp;#197;&amp;#177; lapokat gy&amp;#197;&amp;#177;jt&amp;ouml;t&amp;ouml;k &amp;ouml;ssze magatok el&amp;eacute;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A c&amp;eacute;lotok az lesz, hogy min&amp;eacute;l &amp;uuml;gyesebb kombin&amp;aacute;ci&amp;oacute;kat kompon&amp;aacute;ljatok t&amp;ouml;rt&amp;eacute;net&amp;uuml;nk szerepl&amp;#197;&amp;#145;i, lovai, t&amp;aacute;rgyai &amp;eacute;s helysz&amp;iacute;nei megjelen&amp;iacute;t&amp;eacute;s&amp;eacute;vel. A kezd&amp;#197;&amp;#145;j&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;k sor&amp;aacute;n nagyon gyorsan &amp;eacute;s k&amp;ouml;nnyed&amp;eacute;n elsaj&amp;aacute;t&amp;iacute;thatj&amp;aacute;tok a j&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;k alapjait, amit k&amp;eacute;s&amp;#197;&amp;#145;bb a halad&amp;oacute; m&amp;oacute;dban m&amp;eacute;ly&amp;iacute;thettek el plusz k&amp;aacute;rty&amp;aacute;k &amp;eacute;s &amp;uacute;jabb kombin&amp;aacute;ci&amp;oacute;k seg&amp;iacute;ts&amp;eacute;g&amp;eacute;vel. El&amp;#197;&amp;#145;ker&amp;uuml;lnek a rejt&amp;eacute;lyes titkos k&amp;uuml;ldet&amp;eacute;sek is, amelyekkel tov&amp;aacute;bbi pontokra tehettek szert a j&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;k v&amp;eacute;g&amp;eacute;n, ha teljes&amp;iacute;titek &amp;#197;&amp;#145;ket.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Aki a leg&amp;eacute;rt&amp;eacute;kesebb k&amp;aacute;rtyasort gy&amp;#197;&amp;#177;jt&amp;ouml;tte &amp;ouml;ssze, az nyeri a j&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;kot!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
